narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Cupid Homecare Agency is a In Home Supportive Care provider based in Bronx, NY. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $114.1M in Medicaid payments across 708K claims serving 0 beneficiaries.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: This provider received $114.1M in taxpayer-funded Medicaid payments — enough to fund healthcare for approximately 14,256 Medicaid beneficiaries for a full year at average per-enrollee costs.
